+- Added default path handling to `storage/source_intake/<YYYY-MM-DD>/daily_collection_plan.json`.
+- Added `tests/test_daily_source_collection_runner.py` with tests for:
+  - default output path
+  - custom output_root
+  - valid JSON persistence
